verbose_text: The damage of the organ is connected with an increase of tumor necrosis factor (TNF-alpha) and interleukin 1 beta (IL-1beta) synthesis, activating the nuclear factor kappa-light-chain-enhancer of activated B cells (NF-kappaB) inflammatory signal as well as IL-12 and IL-23, which induce Th1 and Th17 response [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: IL-12 and IL-23, which induce Th1
